     <p>  <strong> !commands</strong> - Show of all commands   </p>
         <p>  <strong>  !restore </strong> - Restore all deleted notes (last 24 hours )   </p>
      <p> <strong>   !removebackups </strong>  - Remove all backup notes (notes gets autobackup when added and gets deleted automatically from backups prior 24 hours)    </p> 
     
          <p>  <strong>   !=$text </strong> - Add a hidden note (replace $text with what you want to hide. e.g !=this is my hidden text)      </p> 
          <p> <strong>  ! </strong> - Show all hidden notes (type only `!` and submit)    </p> 
            <p> <strong>    !removehidden</strong>  - Remove all hidden notes (hidden notes dont get deleted by normal delete so use this to remove hidden)    </p> 
    <p><strong>*Type Commands where you add normal text and submit.</strong></p>
 
